  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>While you wear this enchanted pelt cloak clasped in place by the lupine-like skull, you do not expose any advantages to your foes that would rely on having their allies near you.</p><p>If a creature would benefit from having one of it's allies within 5 feet of you that benefit is nullified. Such features include, but are not limited to: <em>Arcane Advantage</em>, <em>Martial Advantage</em>, <em>Overbearing Pack</em> and <em>Pack Tactics</em>.</p><p>Furthermore, if you play with the <em>Flanking</em> optional rule, you cannot be Flanked; however you can still suffer form being <em>Swarmed</em>.</p>",
